ApplicationProperties.description:
Individual application property settings accessed using Extension.CurrentApplication().
These are key-value pairs that can be retrieved in connector code.
Example: {"MyCustomProperty": "Property value", "AnotherProperty": "Value"}

EnvironmentConfiguration.description:
Individual environment configuration settings accessed using Environment.Configuration().
These are key-value pairs that configure the mashup execution environment.
Example: {"Cloud": "global", "Region": "us-east-1"}

MashupVariables.description:
Mashup variable support accessed using Variable.ValueOrDefault().
These are key-value pairs that will be converted into a string represting a m style record.
Example: {"currentWorkspaceId": "test"}
